<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Donald C. Stewart was professor of English at Kansas State University.</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The Donald C. Stewart collection consists of manuscripts of early drafts of his biography of Fred Newton Scott and collected Newton materials, including correspondence and articles by and about Scott. There are also cassette tape recordings of interviews with individuals who had recollections of Scott.</p>
</scopecontent>

